"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-tennis-1928171-Rafael-Nadal-Olympics-retirement\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Rafael Nadalhas confirmed that he will take a break from tennis after theOlympicsto decide what the future holds for him.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 123, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The 38-year-old is widely expected to retire at the end of the season but is yet to reveal when he will bring the curtain down on his glittering career.Nadal is representing Spain at the Olympics and could faceNovak Djokovicin the second round of the men's singles competition,but a recent injury has cast doubt over whether he will compete.\", \"from\": 124, \"to\": 465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 298, \"end\": 303, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.9990202996832572, \"rank\": 0.000975858856887649, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain_national_football_team\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He is also set to join forces withCarlos Alcarazto go for gold in the men's doubles, with the tennis events being staged at Roland Garros.The veteran Spaniard reached the final of the Swedish Open earlier this month to ensure he will go into the Olympics with plenty of positive momentum.\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 754, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 616, \"end\": 624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"score\": 0.9759267968647886, \"rank\": 0.024567663922333935, \"text\": \"Spaniard\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spaniards\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Thursday, he was quizzed on what lies ahead following the Games and revealed that he would be taking a break to regroup.\", \"from\": 755, \"to\": 878, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Our community members are treated to special 